Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.05,0:00:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Key...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Key... and card...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The PIN...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.68,0:00:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the safety deposit box...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is my experimental data and a tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.31,0:00:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an interview... of a young boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the monster that led Kinderheim 511...\Ndown the path of destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:03.60,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(338,0)\pos(360,365)}The Adventures of Mr. Steiner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.54,Location,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(219,0)\pos(360,384)}Prague Police Station
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Zeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first man to arrive at\Nyesterday's murder scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Grimmer, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry you had to stay the night at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped my nail clippers, under the desk, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When your body's so big, \Nyou bump into a lot of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty big yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bump into a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Zeman, the lead investigator in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I was in the middle of clipping\Nmy nails, so I'm going to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife gets on my case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I let my nails grow, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't let me have any white showing on my nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, I feel like I always have ingrown nails...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday must have been terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought something like that would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you're a freelance journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know anything about his personal history?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikhail Ivanovich Petrov...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real name, Reinhard Biermann.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A German.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the unification of Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was accused of civil rights oppression,\Nslave labor, child abuser and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately after the Berlin Wall came down,\Nhe escaped to the Czech Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Germany wanted to prosecute him but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the authorities in the Czech Republic left him\Nalone while continuing to monitor him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the disturbing elements of\Nthe old Czechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret police?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember how violently they oppressed thought and\Nspeech in this country during the Cold War, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, they were involved with and provided weapons for\Nextreme leftist terrorist acts throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the separation and democratization of the Czech\NRepublic and Slovakia was carried out rather calmly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they went underground without being indicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that Petrov was in contact with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For instance, Petrov could've sold them his information...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're ingrown again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you happen to see a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that Petrov's killer was a young woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, she's apparently really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The children said they passed a woman\Nin front of the house, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those children...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to those orphans Mr. Petrov took in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're keeping them at the station\Nfor the time being, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,starting today, a few of them are going\Nto be taken in by orphanages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry you had to get caught up in all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what kind of information were you trying to collect?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, it's like what you just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just some questions regarding Mr. Petrov, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to learn anything from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just about to, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now my wife won't get mad at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, feel free to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to have kept you here for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As he was dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did Mr. Petrov have any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miroslav... Josef...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, where is Tomas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like all three of you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, get in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on! Hurry up and get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three to the Vinohrady Nursery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honza, Antonin, Izzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be lonely now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were getting along so well,\Nbut now you're splitting up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you'll be separated, you'll\Nstill all be under the same sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A day will come when you guys\Ncan play soccer together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up, Antonin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the leader, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still write them letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should become the center of the\Ngroup and cheer everyone up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the Hotel Kafka...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, the Proch{\fnMeiryo U}á{\fnNarkisim}zka Bank first, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Proch{\fnMeiryo UI}á{\fnNarkisim}zka Bank is on the way to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I don't speak Czech very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you speak German or English?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:08:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's nice today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you stopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can share the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the Svoboda industrial area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should at least ask me before\Npicking up someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see the soccer game on TV yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they didn't do very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we going so far away from town?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hotel is in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Key.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Key!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I followed you because I thought \N you might be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably from the former\Nsecret police I told you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they demand anything from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they'd go this far just for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, really. Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you aren't hiding anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have some idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They really went pretty far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I really don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you've already removed it from\Nthe safety deposit box at the bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cassette tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're looking for his roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roots...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The roots of the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll fetch a high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll know immediately if we listen to the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the Czech Republic the\Nmonster's mother lives, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Inspector Zeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that supermarket robbery suspect...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he give up any of his accomplices?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work, Detective Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have some errands I need to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see I think I can return to\Nthe station in about an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't stop there he won't be able to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel like talking now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I have no idea what you're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing in it for you even\Nif you hide it Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the key to the safety deposit\Nbox you got from Petrov?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I already said, I can't tell you what I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you want money
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much would you sell it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm a third-rate journalist...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not hurting to put food on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look how long your nails are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you my wife is very fussy about these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When your nails get long...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's best if you don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else I'll cut the nail too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you open the safety deposit box at the bank\Nwith the key and get the tape and documents...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have no use for either of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:15:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tape is only meaningful when it\Nis in the hands of their organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of their goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of resurrecting the East!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monster's identity is recorded on that tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They need that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is capable of unifying them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The alumni of Kinderheim 511, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to gather the \Nalumni of Kinderheim 511...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ones who were raised in old East Germany,\Nfor the health and prosperity of communism.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody is more qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that the monster had all of\NKinderheim 511 under his control...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then destroyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who can unify that group of elites!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where is the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Group of elites, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want money, I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a capitalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love money!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm merely trying to earn a lot of\Nmoney by selling them the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The justice of society?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'd go this far for something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were a journalist from the East, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,most of them were intelligence gatherers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, the majority of them were spies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you sent from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to be like 007?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to torture or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about... "The Amazing Steiner"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the 60's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was a cartoon on TV in West Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in East Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to secretly watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main character...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was normally a weak guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when he was in a tight spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,help would always come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His secret friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the main character didn't realize it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That his secret friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was in fact himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main character...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when placed in absolute danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would transform into "The Amazing Steiner"...\Nwho was scary just to look at...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the main character realized it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the bad guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were beaten to a pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and transform, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dump some water on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll spill it eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman came in...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,came in, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One gunshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One man shot to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other two bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had no bullet wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Amazing Steiner, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.93,0:22:31.10,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:44.53,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:44.53,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.53,0:22:47.49,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:23:01.17,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:23:01.17,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:26.03,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:34.45,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.45,0:23:36.91,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
